assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Imasen Electric Industrial Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, develops, manufactures, and sells auto parts in Japan and internationally. It also manufactures and sells industrial machinery parts, health machinery and equipment, such as powerless walking support machines. The company offers power seat adjuster, rear combination lamp, and electromagnetic swirl horn products. In addition, it offers DC converter, power seat/seat heater control ECU, and backup power supply related products. Further, the company provides electric wheelchair, rapok prosthesis, walking support machine, aircraft wire harness, and wire harness for machine tools. Additionally, the company develops, manufactures, and sells industrial cameras and image processing boards. The company manufactures and sells molds, jigs, and other machinery. Imasen Electric Industrial Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1939 and is based in Inuyama, Japan.
